If no year specified, default to 118 (current Congress).

KEYWORDS:
- Extract 2-6 word search terms
- Use formal language (e.g., "artificial intelligence" not "AI")
- Include policy areas (e.g., "defense", "cybersecurity", "healthcare")
- Include specific bill numbers if mentioned (e.g., "H.R. 1234")

RESULT LIMIT:
- 20-50: Narrow topics (specific bills, small committees)
- 50-100: Medium topics (topic area like "AI bills")
- 100-250: Broad topics (large policy areas like "defense authorization")

